== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2012年3月，[[哥倫比亞影業|哥倫比亞影業]]獲得小說三部曲的電影改編版權時，監製{{link-en|葛拉罕·金|Graham King}}及[[陶比·麥奎爾|陶比·麥奎爾]]成為了電影的製作人<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20696355,00.html|title=Book Review: The 5th Wave|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=May 3, 2013|accessdate=5 December 2013|author=Vilkomerson, Sara|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006082324/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20696355,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thewrap.com/j-blakeson-set-to-direct-sony-young-adult-sci-fi-movie-the-5th-wave/|last=Dickey|first=Josh|title=J Blakeson Set to Direct Sony Young-Adult Sci-Fi Movie "The 5th Wave"|accessdate=February 15, 2015|work=The Wrap|date=September 3, 2013|archive-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806064125/https://www.thewrap.com/j-blakeson-set-to-direct-sony-young-adult-sci-fi-movie-the-5th-wave/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月15日，電影公司正式宣布[[克蘿伊·摩蕾茲|嘉兒·莫蕊茲]]將會飾演主角凱西·沙利文，而{{link-en|蘇珊娜·葛蘭特|Susannah Grant}}則會撰寫劇本，電影由{{link-en|J·布萊克森|J Blakeson}}執導<ref name="ew" /><ref>{{cite web|last=Kay|first=Jeremy|title=Chloe Grace Moretz to star in alien invasion drama The 5th Wave|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/production/chloe-moretz-to-ride-sonys-wave/5070748.article?blocktitle=HEADLINES&contentID=40295|work=Screen Daily|publisher=Screen International|accessdate=April 16, 2014|date=April 15, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061106/http://www.screendaily.com/news/production/chloe-moretz-to-ride-sonys-wave/5070748.article?blocktitle=HEADLINES&contentID=40295|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年6月至8月，[[尼克·羅賓森|尼克·羅賓森]]及[[阿萊克斯·羅|阿萊克斯·羅]]分別以男主角本·帕里什及伊雲·沃克的身分加入電影，而[[李佛·薛伯|李佛·薛伯]]則飾演反派人物<ref name="wrap" /><ref name="variety" />。在接下來隨後的幾個月裡，[[瑪嘉·夢露|瑪嘉·夢露]]、{{link-en|札克瑞·亞瑟|Zackary Arthur}}、[[東尼·雷佛羅里|東尼·雷佛羅里]]、[[榮·利文斯通|榮·利文斯通]]、{{link-en|瑪姬·席夫|Maggie Siff}}及[[特麗莎·貝特曼|特麗莎·貝特曼]]加入了這部電影<ref name=siff /><ref name="hollywoodreporter" /><ref name="thewrap" /><ref name="revolori" />。

=== 拍攝 ===
電影於2014年10月18日在[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]的[[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]取景進行[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Rae Johnson|first=Alexa|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2799286/chloe-moretz-dresses-school-uniform-begins-filming-upcoming-sci-fi-drama-5th-wave.html|title=Chloe Moretz dresses in school uniform as she begins filming hotly anticipated sci-fi drama The 5th Wave|accessdate=October 20, 2014|work=Daily Mail|date=October 19, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202423/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2799286/chloe-moretz-dresses-school-uniform-begins-filming-upcoming-sci-fi-drama-5th-wave.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Lesnick|first=Silas|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=124367|title=Production Begins on The 5th Wave, Starring Chloe Grace Moretz|accessdate=October 24, 2014|work=ComingSoon.net|date=October 23, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027124835/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=124367|dead-url=no}}</ref>。三個月後的1月11日，電影在[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]][[梅肯_(喬治亞州)|梅肯]]市中心的一個公車爆炸計劃中，由於計劃差錯而導致其影響範圍甚廣，使棉花大道（Cotton Avenue）的四十個以上的窗戶被毀，還有坍塌的天花板，和店舖門面被毀，並在一個建築物點火，在建築物的磚牆上留下煙灰。電影製作公司承諾會承擔凌晨3:45事件所造成的所有損失，但是所做的工作做得很糟糕，並在28個月後仍未完成<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macon.com/2015/01/11/3524656/movie-explosion-damages-downtown.html|title=Movie explosion damages downtown Macon buildings|work=macon|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115092955/http://www.macon.com/2015/01/11/3524656/movie-explosion-damages-downtown.html|archive-date=2015-01-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/maconsbookstore/status/688025773685497856 |title=Golden Bough Books Twitter |quote=@edunwody @gafmde @5thWaveMovie we expect gold leafing to start any day now but there's unfinished & substandard work on several storefronts |accessdate=2019-08-06 |archive-date=2019-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024144221/https://twitter.com/maconsbookstore/status/688025773685497856 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。拍攝於2015年1月17日正式結束<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fashionnstyle.com/articles/41514/20150117/the-5th-wave-wraps-filming-chloe-grace-moretz-posts-pics-from-set-sci-fi-flick.htm|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150214114913/http://www.fashionnstyle.com/articles/41514/20150117/the-5th-wave-wraps-filming-chloe-grace-moretz-posts-pics-from-set-sci-fi-flick.htm|dead-url=yes|archive-date=February 14, 2015|title='The 5th Wave' Wraps Filming, Chloe Grace Moretz Posts Pics From Set Of Sci-Fi Flick|accessdate=February 13, 2015|work=Fashion&Style|date=January 17, 2015}}</ref>。

